is a modern graphical user interface for neutron and X-ray reflectometry analysis.
The unique item-based model editor allows for an intuitive description of the system under study.
The reflectometry calculation can be performed by BornAgain, refl1d, or refnx.

refnx for making fantastic open-source packages.
